Create a Route53 HealthCheck that monitors a CloudWatch Alarm.

Example Example:

```
const alarm new Alarm(stack, "Alarm", {
  // ...
});
new AlarmHealthCheck(stack, "HealthCheck", {
  alarm: alarm,
});
```

